  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我昨天发了一篇文章，中间有一个观点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就是AI时代，你的产品，可能得同时为了人类和Agent共同设计。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我前几天出去给人分享的时候，在PPT上也写过这个判断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5157407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196997\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23464de3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqWWEQvml5wj6lozX0icgkYZb0fUKicxNMVDDYNju4JNIEoBDdkvP0wR1M9ia6Dlm3q0Ea5XzrOJGTcqtoTXmPAZda1oeIFpR8hutc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">未来的很多产品，可能都会是两个入口并存。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一边是为人类而设计的UI界面，一边是纯粹为了Agent而设计的Skills。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而昨晚，Liblib发了一个他们的AI视频产品，我觉得非常有意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，他们的产品，应该是我第一个看到的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">为人和Agent共同而设计的AI视频产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而且，用一种很优雅的姿态，解决了一个在交互设计领域一直以来都很绝望的问题，就是怎么同时兼顾专业用户和普通用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个东西，名叫LibTV。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">网址在此：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://www.liblib.tv/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liblib.tv/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"500197023\" data-ratio=\"0.5824074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4feb2663&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqU2sUFPXE8H5JIQ6kGDntR4AzHs3bfEmYrJQCHJjlaZqI9SLF0HU6YSicNRMqwJmeMglkPVvaGNL4RzyjyStCFbpZ3fevfr12Wk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个产品，让我一时间，不知道从哪下笔。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为，这玩意真的就是面向人类和Agent双向出击。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给人类用的，就是极度全面、复杂、专业、需要连线和节点的无限画布。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给Agent用的，就是一个使用起来极度简单、无需理解、开箱即用的SKills。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先说这个给人类用的无限画布。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先给大家看一个工作界面，这是一个大佬叫毕加索隆，在上面做的片子《</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">索拉里斯之船</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">》，我非常喜欢这个片子和他的艺术风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而这，这是他的画布界面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看的我脑壳疼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196998\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cd1c7e3a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVcR0yK1I0oOQ5yokP5w51CprhLmG7JMqGRrFrYLBQSCeKQUJaQlL1M2sNvQGNUf4s1PN1nXBcyt0V5DUsuyRXy4IXcfLYbtmc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就咋说呢...虽然节点式的画布看着复杂，对普通用户来说确实有点难上手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是我觉得只要是希望能创作最顶级AI短片AI广告的那些专业创作者，我相信他们绝对会喜欢这个产品，因为，真的太顶了，你能想象到的一切功能，LibTV都给你做了上去。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">支持剧本、图片、视频、音频全链路。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6113074204946997\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"849\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500196999\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9a08c8a9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVDmgRgDtAeebxj3nfTDj5HelPXo5KKmibsTZYeiafwxNiake9hbrJqvbNRIZIDDibhuR7AgpPBzE08Nib9mfkHGibJXsaFJRABHJia4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以，一口气，直接在这里面，完成所有素材的制作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，生成图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5555555555555556\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197003\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c3feaee&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F2jjfQoZLoqVSbjI8FDRB0PYznfzI3dQQFGOXkAfZzm8MUWtic3icWibgoc2OYP6GmutnzA6uL7OnVXvnJ5BypJmAoWSjZdazE78FPcGtIqF2J0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，你也可以自己传一张图片上去，进行处理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而LibTV这个画布，对图片的处理，我感觉就是变态级的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">高清、扩图、重绘、擦除、抠图这些都正常做了，自不必说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43137254901960786\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"867\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197004\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11142c67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUERP9WdvUdWealdnwhVV38JqJCZVsBZajib7So1AaXHBxR7jYM0xL1FhC4libJCIHcM8ibBoj14wsaWibs52yXXytRyzoIY4teHxY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有两个他们雕花雕的很有趣的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个是多角度，直接就预设好了一堆的视角，你一张图扔进去了，就非常非常便捷的，可以出任意视角的图，而且稳定性极高，左边的3D的预览做的也非常有意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.801\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197006\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9f2f875&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqUYXYKJq7YQxoeD0LupyKNIhvCLeJxDfxjeicMHRoGlj5hfG6327icWa56Dj7Zr57k2WCSaamGuFRVhL8WO0OSic082CpSAQWzp9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个是灯光。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6786427145708582\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1002\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197007\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63045d85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqVZtGvAfibnKTI437KVxOgHFQicl4AicDr0neD8DIRJMefdlmxavC3bbprUgYFxcNicY9vJwSgJdFqVWZLUVGyNyCLmRqAVJNoBqVA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，一键改成各种角度的光，极其稳定，轮廓光也能生成。效果非常好，我就随手改了一个右侧50%亮度带有轮廓光的打光，还有一个左侧的75%亮度的效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而当你想继续用这张图生成后续的内容的时候。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你就可以引用这张图，反推Prompt成文本，或者图生图，或者生视频，等等等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7158908507223114\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"623\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500197008\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e50a3162&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2jjfQoZLoqW67IfvfNdwZeM5Xe9dt76jBAn5RuSDymZXfJSzagRqXtghqO9xKibCKPNn6xgkZtAkUBdjf9BkJ1VZyJn7xGDnnzf66a2biavnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我们选择继续生图，你就能看到一个非常多功能的输入框。</span></span></p>\n  <p st